<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 02 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其實啊，<delay20 />
我跟<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" />借了個東西，
但是一直沒機會還給<gender3 m="他" f="她" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那傢伙<delay8 />肯定在生氣吧……<delay frames="40" />
