這時候正在擔心啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay8 />
<anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嗯……<delay8 />我該怎麼辦啊？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="player" targetSpec="" />我幫你送過去吧！</message>
	<message label="002_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="player" targetSpec="" />晚點再送過去吧？</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 02 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好像有人搞錯了，<delay8 />
